title: Dirty Not Sorry @ The Skyline Lounge
description:
Join us at the brand new SKYLINE Lounge @ Temple Saturday! Enjoy breathtaking 360-degree views from our brand new rooftop perch in the heart of downtown. Stay tuned for an exciting lineup of events on the roof; you're not going to want to miss these intimate shows under the San Francisco skyline.

On Saturday, May 6th - Join us on the roof, and come dance with Dirty Not Sorry DJs:

- AANSTER

- ADXRE

- EYEZICK

- MELEVATE

- TAE TAE

- WRAITH

Capacity is extremely limited! RSVP required. Admitted on a first-come-first-served-basis. Early arrival strongly advised.

Skyline Lounge @ Temple is a 21+ venue.

For VIP / Bottle Service, please contact: vip@templesf.com

For more info, please visit: www.TempleSF.com
